description: Bacon's BBQ is one of the best places you will ever find. Since early 2010 their determination to make the best barbecue in Northern Virginia has lead them on a successful road. Sharing homemade recipes with their mobile kitchen catering to any event bringing the best in smoked ribs and charbroiled chicken. Head on over and conquer your hunger with a dish from Bacon's BBQ!
name: Bacon's BBQ
